quran[25{c,v,t}:
76,26,"raat ko bhi is ke huzoor sajda raiz ho, aur raat ke taweel auqaat mein uss ki tasbeeh karte raho"
76,27,yeh log to jaldi haasil honay wali cheez ( duniya ) se mohabbat rakhtay hain aur agay jo bhaari din anay wala hai usay nazar andaaz kar dete hain
76,28,"hum ne hi inn ko peda kya hai aur un ke joor band mazboot kiye hain, aur hum jab chahain inn ki shaklon ko badal kar rakh den"
76,29,"yeh aik nasiyaat hai, ab jis ka jee chahay apne Rab ki taraf jaane ka rasta ikhtiyar kar le"
76,30,aur tumahray chahanay se kuch nahi hota jab taq Allah nah chahay yaqeenan Allah bara Aleem o hakeem hai
76,31,"apni rehmat mein jis ko chahta hai daakhil karta hai, aur zaalmon ke liye is ne dard naak azaab tayyar kar rakha hai"
77,1,qasam hai unn ( hawaon ) ki jo pay Dur pay bhaije jati hain
77,2,phir tofani raftaar se chalti hain
77,3,aur ( baadalon ko ) utha kar phailaati hain
77,4,phir ( unn ko ) phaar kar judda karti hain
77,5,phir ( dilon mein khuda ki ) yaad daalti hain
77,6,izr ke tor par ya draway ke tor par
77,7,jis cheez ka tum se wada kya ja raha hai woh zaroor waqay honay wali hai
77,8,phir jab setaaray maand par jayen ge
77,9,aur aasman phaar diya jaye ga
77,10,aur pahar dhanak daaley jayen ge
77,11,aur Rasolo-n ki haazri ka waqt aa puhanche ga ( is roz woh cheez waqay ho jaye gi )
77,12,kis roz ke liye yeh kaam utha rakha gaya hai ?
77,13,faislay ke roz ke liye
77,14,aur tumhe kya khabar ke woh faislay ka din kya hai ?
77,15,tabahi hai uss din jhutlanay walon ke liye
77,16,kya hum ne uglo ko halaak nahi kya ?
77,17,phir aُnhi ke peechay hum baad walon ko chalta karen ge
77,18,mujrimon ke sath hum yahi kuch kya karte hain
77,19,tabahi hai uss din jhutlanay walon ke liye
